Hey Nepotu! I just came back home from Baja California it was my uncles Birthday. I see you posted Orlando's last game from march 3 of here. I have a million thank you's my friend I wanted to watch this game and was thinking about it last night! thanks for the hookup do you have a paypal account I want to send you a few bucks..You've been keeping me up on the best orlando magic games that I wouldn't be able to watch anywhere else! Thank you Sir

Dante From Travel Channel's Soul Seekers

You're welcome, my dear friend SoulSeekers. I'm happy to help you and other people. Also thank you very much for your wish to donate but I haven't a paypal account and I don't worth it. It's true that I need a computer upgrade and also I'm unemployed (the crisis) but I don't want my friend's money. And Happy birthday to your uncle from Europe!
PS: You are really Dante Reeder from Travel's Channel Soul Seekers???
Yes I am the Real Dante. Soul Seekers we are Ghost Hunters- Sorry for the delay nepotu I wasn't even aware you responded..
